high_descs: Move to the table with the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug next to the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the sink.
Clean the mug in the sink.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the white table across the room.
Pick up the coffee cup that's next to the coffee maker.
Turn to the left and head to the sink across the room.
Wash the coffee cup in the sink on the right.
Turn around and head back to the white table across the room.
Set the coffee cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean coffee cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: walk on over to the right side of the kitchen table
grab the dirty coffee cup off of the table
walk on over to the kitchen sink
place the cup inside the sink and clean it, then pick it back up
walk back over to the kitchen table
place the cup to be directly underneath the coffee makers pouring spout
anns.task_desc: clean the coffee cup to be used again
